longBusinessSummary: Joshua Gold Resources Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for gold and graphite deposits. The company has the rights to twelve mineral properties in Ontario and in the Northwest Territories, Canada. The company was formerly known as Enhanced Energy Solutions Corp. and changed its name to Joshua Gold Resources Inc. in October 2016. Joshua Gold Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Woodstock, Canada.
